Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:47.53,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}总会有一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.67,0:02:50.62,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}飘落下来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.70,0:02:56.42,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}属于我的蓝色天使啊{\fnMS Gothic}…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:03:03.13,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}啊　那擦肩而过的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:08.16,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}弯下身去发现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.17,0:03:15.00,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}转身去呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:21.34,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}现在的内心里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:26.17,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}就像雪一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:28.70,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}堆积起了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.96,0:03:33.27,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}纯真的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:38.37,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}就算绕了些远
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.63,0:03:40.95,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}这份思念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:46.31,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}也想直接亲口告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.05,0:03:49.27,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}总会有一日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.09,0:03:52.97,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}飞向蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:58.26,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}属于我的蓝色天使啊{\fnMS Gothic}…
Dialogue: 2,0:02:45.56,0:02:47.53,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}いつからか
Dialogue: 2,0:02:48.67,0:02:50.62,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}舞い降りた
Dialogue: 2,0:02:51.70,0:02:56.42,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}私の蒼い天使よ…
Dialogue: 2,0:02:57.65,0:03:03.13,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}Ah　すれ違う微笑みに
Dialogue: 2,0:03:04.00,0:03:08.16,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}うつむくしかできずに
Dialogue: 2,0:03:10.17,0:03:15.00,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}背中ごしに声かけたの
Dialogue: 2,0:03:15.18,0:03:21.34,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}今は心の中で
Dialogue: 2,0:03:21.43,0:03:26.17,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}それは雪のように
Dialogue: 2,0:03:26.37,0:03:28.70,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}降りつもった
Dialogue: 2,0:03:28.96,0:03:33.27,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}イノセントな痛み
Dialogue: 2,0:03:33.60,0:03:38.37,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}たとえ遠まわりでも
Dialogue: 2,0:03:38.63,0:03:40.95,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}この想いは
Dialogue: 2,0:03:41.30,0:03:46.31,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}まっすぐ届けたい
Dialogue: 2,0:03:47.05,0:03:49.27,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}いつの日か
Dialogue: 2,0:03:50.09,0:03:52.97,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}飛びたってゆけ
Dialogue: 2,0:03:53.29,0:03:58.26,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}私の蒼い天使よ…
